    "body": "<!-- Checklist for reporting a bug\r\n- Check the issue tracker. The issue you have may have already been reported.\r\n- Ensure you have tested the latest developers version.\r\n-->\r\n\r\n**Describe the bug**\r\n<!-- A clear and concise description of what the bug is. -->\r\nThere is a scenario where the bottom navigation view completely disappears / never re enter's again / not available for the user.\r\n\r\n**Expected behavior**\r\n<!-- A clear and concise description of what you expected to happen. -->\r\nThe bottom navigation view shouldn't disappear and should be available to the user for navigation always.\r\n\r\n**Steps to reproduce the behavior:**\r\n1. Navigate to library screen\r\n2. Have at most items/books where the scrolling behaviour of the bottom view is just enabled (5 items in my case).\r\n3. Delete an item when the bottom navigation view is scrolled away\r\n4. Bottom navigation view is lost ;( , hence user cannot navigate.\r\n\r\n**Reason**\r\nIf we delete an item when the bottom view is scrolled away and the scrolling of the recycler view is disabled/stopped due to less no of items ,the bottom view cannot come back / re enter\r\n\r\n**Screen Recording**\r\n<!-- If applicable, add screenshots to help explain your problem otherwise delete this heading. -->\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/kiwix/kiwix-android/assets/111702455/1e378d17-c750-4617-ac25-2de43522f2ad\r\n\r\n\r\n**Environment**\r\n- Version of Kiwix Android : 3.7.1 develop version\r\n- Device : Realme 3i\r\n- OS version : 10\r\n",
